name: MultiPlanetary Inus
description: MultiPlanetary $INUS is the first-ever token unifying the top meme coin communities in our P2E MMORPG. Players will be able to play the game and earn $INUS tokens and purchase NFTs. Different types of NFTs will boost character attributes. Following the vision of the Dogefather, each and every Inu will be able to transport themselves through multiple planets. Clan together, build your planet, strategize and prepare for battle.
